posting_body: ["Our Beautiful Mediterranean Village Apartment Homes are centrally located to The Beverly Center, Cedars-Sinai, The Grove and a new Trader Joe's.", 'We offer amenities to improve your quality of living including a 24 hour Gym, year-round resort-style heated pool, A/C, gated-covered-assigned parking, and controlled access entry.', 'Come meet our on-site professional management team.', '- Courtyard setting with tropical landscape, fountains, and koi pond', '- Heated resort-style pool', '- 24-Hour fitness center', '- 24-Hour laundry centers', '- Elevator access', '- Gas included', '- Cable and high-speed internet available', '- Walking distance to Melrose Avenue shopping district', '- Walking distance to the Beverly Center', '- Walking distance to Santa Monica and Sunset Boulevard’s dining and grocery shopping', '- 2 miles from The Grove and The Farmers Market', '- Steps to public transportation', '- Conveniently located to the 405, 10, and 101 freeways', '- Gated property access', '- Assigned covered parking', '- On-site management available 7 days a week', '- 24-Hour emergency on-call maintenance', '- Nightly courtesy patrol', '- Air conditioning', '- Mirrored closets', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', '*On select units and new move-ins only.', 'Pricing is subject to change.', 'Restrictions apply.', 'Call for details.']
